{"URN":[{"def":"A measure of capacity for liquids, containing about three gallons and a haft, wine measure.","pos":""},{"def":"A hollow body shaped like an urn, in which the spores of mosses are contained; a spore case; a theca.","pos":""}],"URN-SHAPED":[{"def":"Having the shape of an urn; as, the urn-shaped capsules of some mosses.","pos":""}],"URNAL":[{"def":"Of or pertaining to an urn; effected by an urn or urns.","pos":""}],"URNFUL":[{"def":"As much as an urn will hold; enough to fill an urn.","pos":""}]}